dct_description_sm: "8/42/G.S.G.S." "Published by War Office 1942." "Army Map Service, U. S. Army, Washington, D. C. 103041. 1943. 2-43." "British North West Africa Grid." "Grid North is 5°41ʹ E. of True North on this sheet." Map shows gas works, water supplies, churches, mosques, and cemeteries of different religions. "For continuation Westwards to road junction at Le Bardo see inset below." With key to figures.
dct_creator_sm: Great Britain. War Office. General Staff. Geographical Section
dct_publisher_sm: [London] : War Office. General Staff Geographical Section, 1942.
Washington, D.C. : Army Map Service, U.S. Army, 1943.
